	* res_rtp_asterisk:  Avoid close the rtp/rtcp fd twice.

	  When RTCP-MUX enabled. rtp->s is the same as rtcp->s, check this before
	  close the file descriptor. Close the FD twice will hangs the asterisk
	  under heavy load.

