	  Change-Id: Ie53e1997104cd2674821688b8a8247249f5e156f

2016-08-18 08:14 +0000 [3eb02235f5]  Alexander Traud <pabstraud@compuserve.com>

	* sip_to_pjsip: Parse register even with transport.

