	  Change-Id: Ibb004eda37a14c0a35ef0613f6237977fc800037

2016-06-23 04:33 +0000 [6e87bf746a]  Alexander Traud <pabstraud@compuserve.com>

	* BuildSystem: Avoid obsolete warning with AC_TYPE_SIGNAL on autoconf.

