2014-08-06 12:55 +0000 [r420124]  Kinsey Moore <kmoore@digium.com>

	* configs/samples/stasis.conf.sample (added), main/named_acl.c,
	  apps/app_queue.c, main/stasis_bridges.c, main/loader.c,
