2014-03-28 17:41 +0000 [r411515-411530]  Matthew Jordan <mjordan@digium.com>

	* rest-api/api-docs/channels.json,
	  rest-api/api-docs/recordings.json,
	  rest-api/api-docs/endpoints.json, rest-api/api-docs/events.json,
