2014-03-08 16:50 +0000 [r410288]  George Joseph <george.joseph@fairview5.com>

	* res/res_pjsip/config_auth.c, /, res/res_pjsip/location.c,
	  res/res_pjsip_outbound_registration.c,
	  res/res_pjsip_endpoint_identifier_ip.c,
